<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195508>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 6. Adults of Chrysoteuchia spp. 3. C. rotundiprojecta sp. n., holotype, male; 4. C. nonifasciaria sp. n., paratype, female; 5. C. furva sp. n., holotype, male; 6. C. shafferi sp. n, holotype, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.195509>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 10. Male genitalia of Chrysoteuchia spp. 7. C. rotundiprojecta sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 07019; 8. C. nonifasciaria sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08443; 9. C. furva sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08450; 10. C. shafferi sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08447 (scales: 0.5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/195509/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

